name: Stained glass Taurus unveils
description:
Watch the zodiac sign being revealed.   

Stained glass has always been a sign of happiness as it brings colorful light to dark places. It is playful, and just for that mixing it with a puzzle-like game makes it even more lively.   
With The Bull as its symbol, Taurus is the second zodiac sign among the twelve zodiac signs. People born from 19th April to 20th May are considered Taurus natives. The element of Taurus is 'Earth'. Every zodiac has its qualities based on its element. Taurus is considered Cold and Dry as it has Earth element. The zodiac quality of Taurus is considered 'Fixed'. Being a Fixed sign, Taurus natives are practical and cautious in their life.
